2026-04-22T02:14:57.2899533Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-22T02:14:57.2900715Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-22T02:14:57.2901686Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-22T02:14:57.2902651Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-22T02:14:57.2903599Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-22T02:14:57.2904568Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-22T02:14:57.2905514Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
