2026-04-22T02:14:57.5070882Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-04-22T02:14:57.5071511Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-22T02:14:57.5072302Z 25            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-22T02:14:57.5073080Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-22T02:14:57.5073848Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-22T02:14:57.5074608Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-22T02:14:57.5075396Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-22T02:14:57.5076156Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-22T02:14:57.5076866Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-22T02:14:57.5077426Z 32    -->
